<emphasis id="50ADEAC5FF9A2477FF13FB760E1705C0" bold="true" box="[176,351,1159,1188]" pageId="51" pageNumber="336">Distribution.</emphasis>
S New Guinea (Western Province in Papua New Guinea) and NE Australia (N Queensland), mostly near sea level.
</paragraph>
